        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued April 4 at 12:22AM CDT by NWS Midland/Odessa TX</headline>
        <description>At 1222 AM CDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm 13
miles northwest of Reagan County Airport, or 14 miles northwest of
Big Lake, moving northeast at 50 mph.

HAZARD...Nickel size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor hail damage to vegetation is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Saint Lawrence, Best, Garden City, and Stiles.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
